data.description: Quiet country setting nestled in attractive Hidden Oaks subdivision just off Broadway is where you will find this attractive 4 bed 2.5 bath 3 car garage brick home.  Even though this is a Guthrie address, it is located in Edmond School District. The open concept home also offers a split floor plan with the master suite and one guest bedroom on one side and the other 2 guest bedrooms plus bath on the opposite side of the home.  The spacious open living room features hardwood floors, tray ceiling with crown molding, and gas fireplace.  You are going to be pleasantly surprised at the size of the kitchen.  With beautifully stained cabinetry, granite counter, tumbled travertine backsplash and stainless appliances, it also has close to 15 feet of counter surface! A roomy laundry with lots of storage and counter top for folding. Just off living is a flex space for study nook, hobby room or home office.  Located in the 3 car garage is an inground storm shelter. This home is a winner for sure!
